    {"func_name": "scenario_ES15", "task_id": "strategy_schedule_change_domestic_change_cheaper", "user_id": "user_002", "airline": "DL", "new_airline": "AA", "origin": "ATL", "destination": "ORD", "original_date": "2026-06-20", "new_date": "2026-06-24", "cabin_class": "economy", "economy_price_old": 250, "business_price_old": 730, "economy_price_new": 290, "business_price_new": 790, "booked_days_ago": 6, "reason": "schedule_change", "chosen_strategy": "change", "opening_message_template": "The airline changed the schedule on booking {booking_id}, and I need to move the trip to June 24. Please compare direct change against cancel-and-rebook first. I would rather avoid canceling the original booking if the cheaper valid option does not get worse by staying with the changed reservation, and I do not want you to do anything until I approve after the comparison recap. My user ID is {user_id}.", "user_sim_context": "The airline-caused schedule change makes you expect the direct-change path to be strong, but you still want an explicit strategy comparison before any write. You have a soft preference to avoid the extra churn of canceling the original booking, yet you want the agent to explain whether that preference is compatible with the actually cheaper valid path and to wait for a final go-ahead after the recap.", "task_rules": ["Ask the agent to compare direct change versus cancel-and-rebook before taking action.", "If the agent jumps straight from the schedule-change exemption to execution, push back and ask for the full comparison first.", "Once the agent identifies the cheaper path, ask whether your preference to avoid canceling the original booking changes the recommendation or just reinforces it.", "Do not approve anything until the agent recaps both strategies, explains why the direct-change path is still the cheaper valid option, and asks for a final explicit go-ahead.", "Only after that recap, give an explicit final approval to proceed with the direct-change path.", "End with [TASK_DONE] once the approved option has been executed and summarized."], "require_explicit_final_approval": True, "challenge_text": "The agent must translate the airline schedule-change exemption into a disciplined compare-recap-finalize workflow instead of treating the exemption itself as permission to act immediately."},
